{"tid":1526317,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"罷課如何說服中立老豆？","createTime":"2019-09-01T05:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T11:22:53.000Z","uid":297112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b8a64b4305a35071e5cc596326b2cabe58d43f2f","tid":1526317,"uid":297112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:23:28.000Z","msg":"升中五嘅表妹到今日都未敢出聲，有冇咩好計？？幫問。<br />\n<br />\n背景 佢老豆 典型中立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />為人超嚴肅，兩邊都會鬧，唔會畀我表妹出去發夢，唯一一次9/6 同我同表妹一齊遊行。<br />\n<br />\n我會今日試下陪佢一齊開口。我上網淨係揾到哩個家長信sample，有無其他意見？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/226258934521376/posts/717954055351859/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F226258934521376%2Fposts%2F717954055351859%2F&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2XyMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=7b9c9af7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/226258934521376/posts/717954055351859/</a><br />\n<br />\n//罷課信範本<br />\n因應要求，我們草擬了9月3日罷課家長信，供有需要的家長參考。<br />\n下載連結： <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/903Stroke\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F903Stroke&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2XyMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=0ae8acce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/903Stroke</a><br />\n<br />\n我們尊重學生有發表意見的自由， 與此同時呼籲學生們有罷課志向時必須要得到家長的同意，有足夠的共識下進行相關決定。<br />\n香港人加油，萬事小心<br />\n<br />\n家長聯盟<br />\n2019年8月31日//"},{"pid":"f072df73820f87382ead9e237ea616fe1a26b227","tid":1526317,"uid":300690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"罷課不罷學。自修"},{"pid":"c588396071843fb8808148e8ab36491211f69c69","tid":1526317,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:25:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"154faf71422a76754ffd1c8bc48bef97b8666d05","